<dl id="n40112e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40112e">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40112e"> 112(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Chrysostome </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Chrysostom (347?-407), Gr. church father; archbishop of Constantinople (398-404): his day is Sept. 13. Named from Classical Greek <i>chrysostomos</i>, golden-mouthed from <i>chrysos</i>, gold + <i>stoma</i>, mouth: an epithet earned for eloquence in preaching</mm> </dd></dl>
